songs.title: I Don’t Need A Man*
songs.lyrics:
[All]
Hell yeah, I am!

[Jesy]
I don't need a man
If I’m lovin' you, it's ’cause I can
I don't want your cash
I put my own rock on my hand
I put my own rock on my hand
I put my own rock on my hand
I don't need a man
If I'm lovin' you, it's 'cause I can

[Jade]
Make way for-
